node.text:
This is Red Bull’s genius marketing play...have you seen any other businesses do something similar?

Credit to @ourfuturehq 
Follow us @businessinstantly

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'ADVICE FOR 20 YEARS OLD "Start multiple business in your 20's. Fail at the first couple and then find one thing to big on" -Kevin o 'Leary let-Worth: $400M BUSINESS INSTANTLY'.

node.text:
Your 20s are prime time to start building a generational empire. You're still young and have time to fail over and over again before finding what works for you.

This is exactly what I did. I started with dropshipping and transitioned into digital marketing by building instagram and other social media pages.

If you have the time take advantage of it!

Follow us @businessinstantly

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'WHERE IT ALL STARTED Apple Google Amazon ማυ..E Harley Disney Lamborghini BUSINESS INSTANTLY'.

node.text:
You don't need a lot to get started. A consistent work ethic and a good mindset will get you farther than a fancy work space.

Disney paid $10 a month for rent to produce videos in the back of a small office...no excuses.

Follow us @businessinstantly

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger In 2012, was taking out loans to feed my addiction on on Silk Road. In 2021, now own a crypto fund with $40M AUM. Here's how we got to this point...'.

node.text:
@jeffsekinger came back from a addiction to now owning multiple 8-figure businesses, one of them being a crypto fund with $40M AUM. You should follow if you want to learn more about credit, funding, or crypto.

Go follow @jeffsekinger 🔥

Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger Corporate was hammering me for posting free finance content. The job also held me me back from what truly wanted out of life, which was freedom and to truly help others, Not just to stack some billionaire's pockets. That's when quit my job and started my first business.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. Since our launch, we've got $40M in the fund and growing.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger Did| get lucky by stumbling on Bitcoin and crypto early? Yeah. Did turn a shitty situation with my addiction into a huge opportunity for me and others? Also, yeah.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger If you want to see more content around fixing your credit and investing in crypto, follow me. You won' be disappointed.'.

node.text:
Who do you think is really behind bitcoin?

Credit to: iletd on TikTok
Follow us @businessinstantly

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BUSINESS INSTANTLY Business Instantly @businessinstantly Idc if have $20,000 in savings and another $20,000 in investments. If my checking says $300 then $300 is all I have!'.

node.text:
It's all about money management. The cash you have is all that matters. Savings and investments that are put away and making money consistently is what's important.

If you have very little in checking its important to keep stacking more cashflow so you can continue investing and watch the money compound.

Follow us @businessinstantly
